{"tid":2070812,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Windows 突更新累死電競選手　CS:GO 大賽反勝為敗痛失124 萬","createTime":"2020-06-19T11:28:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-20T05:55:00.000Z","uid":1886,"like":6,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"e92132b48b97ed6b0b9eccb094a5e92f4e2edf05","tid":2070812,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:28:21.000Z","msg":"相信不少朋友都經歷過 Windows 更新令電腦忽然關機，或者需要等候長時間才能開機的情況。最近有電競賽事在激戰期間忽然令電腦進入更新需要暫停，原先領先的選手後來被反超前輸掉賽事。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/06/18/forced-windows-update-nearly-sabotages-dreamhack-csgo-match/game-channel/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F06%2F18%2Fforced-windows-update-nearly-sabotages-dreamhack-csgo-match%2Fgame-channel%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84C67%2FPCTF2%2B9SGuy7I2Db2XM%3D&h=cd546a2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/06/18/forced-windows-update-nearly-sabotages-dreamhack-csgo-match/game-channel/</a>"},{"pid":"881b1ee4f308f137a2566a132eccc991f49999e9","tid":2070812,"uid":1886,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:28:44.000Z","msg":"出事的比賽是一年一度的 DreamHack Masters Spring，每年都會吸引電競好手透過 Counter Strike: Global Offensive 作賽。今年的賽事原定在瑞士舉辦，但是因為武漢肺炎疫情而需要改為網上進行，分為北美、歐洲、亞洲和大洋洲四個地區。"},{"pid":"563d2dc15beb915e566aa4124d3a8ea8db8576f2","tid":2070812,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:29:03.000Z","msg":"在最近的歐洲區賽事中，法國的 Team Vitality 與瑞典 Ninjas in Pyjamas 對戰期間，雖然以 6 比 2 大幅領先，但忽然 Team Vitality 的成員 ZywOo 電腦忽然開始自動更新，雖然他並未離開伺服器，但是已經無法繼續比賽，需要申請暫停。在完成更新後比賽繼續，Team Vitality 優勢持續並以 16 比 3 完成首場，不過之後兩場 Ninjas in Pyjamas 就連續勝利，令 Team Vitality 反勝為敗，無法晉級，也與 16 萬美元(約124 萬港元)獎金無緣。"},{"pid":"411ec1f34406933b08d944d70a67ca96091caf62","tid":2070812,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T11:29:54.000Z","msg":"NIP"},{"pid":"e57ef3b831b49aaca423ef917ec2d6cd238489d7","tid":2070812,"uid":85586,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":2,"replyTi